"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715617","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-04-18","<p>The Ministry of Defence is in the early stages of considering its future requirements management system. It is likely that existing Crown Commercial Services frameworks will be utilised to compete the future requirement, although the procurement process and associated timings are still being scoped.</p><p> </p><p> </p>","West Worcestershire","Harriett Baldwin","69938 ; 69939 ; 69940","2017-04-18T15:23:01.567Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715617/answer","Biography information for Harriett Baldwin","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715617/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715617/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-03-30","Defence Equipment and Support: Procurement","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, by what procurement process the requirements management and systems engineering tools for Defence Equipment and Support (DES) will be advertised; and whether there will be separate procurement processes for the software tools component and the provision of training and consultancy services for DES.","false","Biography information for John Woodcock","Barrow and Furness","John Woodcock","69946"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715618","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-04-19","<p>The information is not held centrally and could be provided only at disproportionate cost.</p>","Hemel Hempstead","Mike Penning",,"2017-04-19T16:06:29.327Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715618/answer","Biography information for Sir Mike Penning","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715618/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715618/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-03-30","Army: Training","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how many Royal Military Police investigations involving staff there have been at each phase 1 training centre where people aged under 18 were present in each of the last 10 years; what the (a) related allegations and (b) outcomes were of each of those investigations; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Liz Saville Roberts","Dwyfor Meirionnydd","Liz Saville Roberts","69929"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715619","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-04-19","<p>There are 327 Annington Homes Ltd residential properties in the City of York Local Authority area. These properties provide housing for all the Barracks in the area.</p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster",,"2017-04-19T15:25:45.033Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715619/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715619/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715619/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-03-30","Armed Forces: Housing","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how many residential properties managed by Annington there are in each of the City of York local authority area disposal sites referred to in a Better Defence Estate, published by his Department on 7 November 2016.","false","Biography information for Rachael Maskell","York Central","Rachael Maskell","69968"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715620","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-04-18","<p>The Ministry of Defence is in the early stages of considering its future requirements management system. It is likely that existing Crown Commercial Services frameworks will be utilised to compete the future requirement, although the procurement process and associated timings are still being scoped.</p><p> </p><p> </p>","West Worcestershire","Harriett Baldwin","69939 ; 69940 ; 69946","2017-04-18T15:23:01.41Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715620/answer","Biography information for Harriett Baldwin","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715620/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/715620/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-03-30","Ministry of Defence: Procurement","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, if he will make an assessment of the potential cost saving of a competitive tendering process for requirements management systems.","false","Biography information for John Woodcock","Barrow and Furness","John Woodcock","69938"
